  "time_ut": 1661579019,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd3\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc0\u0db1\u0dc3\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dda \u0d85\u0db4\u0dad\u0dba\u0ddd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The bastards of the police destroy the reputation of the police",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "It seems that the police have again become a bad art. A news related to a police station commander who allegedly molested a police constable was reported from Matara district. Even before the heat of the news faded, information about such a lustful Police Station Commander was reported from Ratnapura district. A female police constable had fallen prey to the lustful police chief. It is also stated in the media reports that this lecher forced the police constable to drink boiled water with ganja.",
        "When the police chiefs went astray like that, our newspaper reported a story about four police officers who thought, \"What if we did?\" These four policemen had committed a robbery. It is stated in our news that the four police officers who robbed a young man's gold necklace and an Apple mobile phone at Pannipitiya Vidyalaya Junction were working attached to the Malabe Police. It is further stated in our news that the four left for the robbery in a three-wheeler belonging to one of the arrested police officers.",
        "Senior Superintendent of Police in charge of Nugegoda Division B.G.S. Mr. Jayamaha and Kottawa Police Station Officer Inspector W.A.K. A special tribute should be given to Mr. Subhashana and the other officers who investigated the robbery and arrested the four thieves. The reason for that special praise is that when the information was revealed that the thief was connected to the police, the incident was saved and the police did not protect the name. News has come to light that some police chiefs of the province conducted a big operation to save Kamathura hora kapua in Galle province, who is said to have made crores of money by filming those moments by abusing children and selling them on the internet. In the end, it was also reported that the police department had to conduct a special investigation about that police operation.",
        "It is true that it is very difficult to live on the salary that one receives these days. But in such a case, it is normal to limit expenses to the amount of income. If he cannot live on his salary, it means that his expenses are unlimited.",
        "Among the factors that lead to excessive spending are drinking drugs, going to nightclubs, and going to cheaters. In addition to investigating the robbery of the four policemen, a special investigation should be conducted as to why their expenses were so high. Because these four robbers are police officers.",
        "More than 100,000 people work in the police department. It is clear that the vast majority of them are engaged in a proud and honorable service while preserving the dignity of the uniform. At the same time, there are 'scumbags' who bring indelible infamy to the police department, which stinks up the entire police department. The four policemen who robbed a young man's gold necklace and Apple mobile phone on the street are such scoundrels.",
        "The majority of the people of the country consider the police as the symbol of law. The responsibility of the police is also to maintain law and order. And law enforcement. That is why the police department should stand before the society with a proud personality. If not, people's confidence in the law will be broken. There is no greater tragedy for a country than that. Therefore, the scoundrels who tarnish the name of the police should be given maximum punishment. And they should not be limited to statements."
      ],
